## Usage

### Basic Commands

```bash
# Greet someone
{{project_name}} greet "World"
# Output: Hello, World!

# Greet with options
{{project_name}} greet "Alice" --uppercase --repeat 3
# Output: HELLO, Alice!
# Output: HELLO, Alice!
# Output: HELLO, Alice!

# Show {{project_name}} information
{{project_name}} info
# Output: {{project_name}} v{{project_version}}
```

### Documentation

```bash
# Generate documentation
{{project_name}} docs --format markdown --output docs/

# Generate HTML documentation
{{project_name}} docs --format html --output {{project_name}}.html
```

{{#if with_completions}}
### Shell Completions

```bash
