{{#if with_completions}}
### Shell Completion Setup

#### Bash
```bash
# Add to ~/.bashrc
source <({{project_name}} completions --shell bash)
```

#### Zsh
```bash
# Add to ~/.zshrc
autoload -U compinit && compinit
source <({{project_name}} completions --shell zsh)
```

#### PowerShell
```powershell
# Add to PowerShell profile
{{project_name}} completions --shell powershell | Out-String | Invoke-Expression
```
{{/if}}

## Configuration

Create a configuration file at `~/.config/{{project_name}}/config.toml`:

```toml
